    <strong>IV. Tasks of the Modern Financial Manager:</strong>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>Financial planning and forecasting</li>
      <li>Capital structure design (debt-equity mix)</li>
      <li>Investment appraisal (capital budgeting)</li>
      <li>Working capital management</li>
      <li>Risk management</li>
      <li>Dividend policy formulation</li>
      <li>Relationship with investors, lenders, regulators</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

